.TH VIDMOD-FIT1080 1 "July 7, 2026" "vidmod 2.4.1"
.SH NAME
vidmod-fit1080 \- Fit a video into a centered 1920x1080 black frame
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vidmod fit1080
[\fB-f\fR \fIFFMPEG-OPTIONS\fR] \fIINPUT\fR [\fIOUTPUT\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vidmod fit1080
uses ffmpeg to scale a video down to fit inside 1920x1080 while preserving its
aspect ratio, then pads it into a centered black 1920x1080 frame.

Audio is copied without re-encoding.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-f \fIFFMPEG-OPTIONS\fR
Pass extra ffmpeg options.
.TP
.B \-h
Show usage help.
.TP
.B \-v, --version
Show the plugin name and version.
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Rémino Rem: <https://remino.net/>
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vidmod (1)
